    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "June 26, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Boise, Idaho",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Dear Mr [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "I have just read an account in the Chicago Tribune concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "an aerial train composed of at least 9 units shaped like a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "pie-plate and silvery in color, traveling at 1200 m.p.h. near",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Mount Ranier, as witnessed by you while flying in the vicinity.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "This is quite important to me, because I have in my possession",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "numerous independent confirmations of what you saw, although none",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "in as great detail as your account. I am interested in publishing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "an article in our magazine, written from a personal account by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "yourself, and accompanied by pix of yourself, plane, and rough",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "sketches by yourself, of what you saw.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "If you care to do this for me, I am prepared to pay our usual",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "rates of 2¢ perword, plus $5.00 for each photograph you can",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "provide, or for each sketch which can be used by our art staff",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "to illustrate the article.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Included in this material, we'd like a short biographical",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "sketch of yourself as \"author background\" material. The",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "article would appear under your by-line.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "If you are not interested, I would at least appreciate a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "letter from you, confirming the newspaper story.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Very truly yours,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
